= content_for :title, "Partner"

%header(class="hero partner-hero hero-no-navbar")
    %div(class="partner-hero__container")
        %div(class="partner-hero__grid")
            %div(class="partner-hero__grid-item")
                %div(class="hero__heading")
                    %div(class="hero__heading-eyebrow")
                        %p(class="text text-eyebrow") Partners
                    %div(class="hero__heading-title")
                        %h1(class="text text-xxl text-bold") 
                            Grow your wholesale orders by up to
                            %span(class="hero__heading-highlight") 200%
                    %div(class="hero__heading-caption")
                        %p(class="text text-l text-secondary") Sell direct to consumers and businesses on the e-commerce platform built for scale.
                        -# %p(class="text text-l") We are taking wholesale in a new direction. With advanced technology, transparency, and more opportunities, both buyers and sellers win.
                    %div(class="hero__heading-action")
                        = link_to "Get Free Early Access", new_seller_path, class: "button button-big button-primary"
                    -# %div(class="hero__heading-footer")
                    -#     %p(class="text text-xs text-secondary-light") Due to the impact of COVID-19, Shopify is offering an extended 90-day free trial. By entering your email, you agree to receive marketing emails from Shopify.
            
            %div(class="partner-hero__grid-image")
                = image_tag asset_path('/assets/hero/partner-header.jpg'), 'data-src': asset_path('/assets/hero/partner-header.jpg'), loading: "lazy", class: "lazy"

        %div(class="partner-hero__features")
            %div(class="partner-hero__features-item")
                %div(class="partner-hero__feature")
                    %div(class="partner-hero__feature-icon")
                        = icon "fas", "users"
                    %div(class="partner-hero__feature-heading")
                        %p(class="text text-m text-medium") Single Workspace
                    %div(class="partner-hero__feature-content")
                        %p(class="text text-s") Run your business from anywhere with one dashboard, available on desktop or mobile.
            %div(class="partner-hero__features-item")
                %div(class="partner-hero__feature")
                    %div(class="partner-hero__feature-icon")
                        = icon "fas", "chart-bar"
                    %div(class="partner-hero__feature-heading")
                        %p(class="text text-m text-medium") Analytics
                    %div(class="partner-hero__feature-content")
                        %p(class="text text-s") See real-time and recent activity, gain insight into your visitors, and analyze your business performance.
            %div(class="partner-hero__features-item")
                %div(class="partner-hero__feature")
                    %div(class="partner-hero__feature-icon")
                        = icon "fas", "megaphone"
                    %div(class="partner-hero__feature-heading")
                        %p(class="text text-m text-medium") Marketing
                    %div(class="partner-hero__feature-content")
                        %p(class="text text-s") One platform to find and sell to the right shoppers, wherever they are.



%section(class="section section-page")
    -# %div(class="section-page-block")
    -#     %div(class="content-page")
    -#         %div(class="section-header section-header-center section-header-tight")
